name: Auspicious Treasure Tree
description: This glittering ornamental plant, adorned with a multitude of golden Fortune Coins, is popular among the people of Liyue for its symbolic meaning of "ushering in wealth and prosperity, filling the home with gold and jade."\n"Say, if we fill the courtyard with these Auspicious Treasure Trees, wouldn't the next year be..." is a line frequently heard among enthusiasts who are passionate about displaying them.
